## [1.0.0] - 2017-03-31

Initial commit.

### Added
- project setup
    - README
    - typescript config
    - lint config
- licensed under MIT license
- basic metrics
    - counter
    - gauge
    - histogram
    - meter
    - timer
- basic metric-registry
- logger reporter (console, scheduled)
- mocha testing (with chai, sinon)
- Jenkins pipeline
- basic unit-tests for components
- NYC code-coverage config
